<p>
  <span class="nym">Hippolyta</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A derivative of <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>ἵππος</i> 'horse'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of an Amazonian queen appearing in the Greek myths of Heracles and Theseus.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Shakespeare adapted the mythological character for his play "A Midsummer Night's Dream" (1590x1596).</p>
  
  


